the lakes are also used for event venues ; rotorua hosted the 2007 world waterski championships and lake rotorua was the venue for the world blind sailing championships in march 2009.http://www.sailing.org/news/5825.php ifds world blind sailing champs come to rotorua

world food & drink : many visitors to rotorua in this country enjoy a hangi , a traditional maori feast of steamed meat & vegetables

